# Curated distribution allowlist — the ONLY files that ship to the team harness repo.
# One path per line; a trailing "/" copies a directory recursively. Blank lines and
# lines starting with "#" are ignored. Anything not listed here stays private in the
# source repo (proposals, HANDOFF, DISTRIBUTION, preview.html, storybook internals, …).
# build-dist.mjs also GENERATES: README.md (consumer) + CHANGELOG.md (released versions only).

